scene.message:
Maki: We're going to meet this{nl}
"Queen" person, right?{wait_fr:21}{nl}
...I hope she's not scary.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I think Chisato's{nl}
paintings aren't bad,{nl}
though...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The Queen, hm...{waitkey}{nl}
Come to think of it, Aki was{nl}
saying something about a{nl}
"cute girl."{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: To think Kozai is the{nl}
Harem Queen. Well, I suppose{nl}
it does suit her.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: So now we've finally{nl}
pinned down Kandori's{nl}
whereabouts. But a "castle,"{nl}
of all things...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I never imagined I'd be{nl}
exploring a "haunted house"{nl}
at this age.{waitkey}{clearbox}It wasn't permitted when I{nl}
was a child, after all...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Even the armor shop's{nl}
got an atmosphere that fits{nl}
this town perfectly.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ......{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Go easy on Sonomura,{nl}
would you.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: You know, don't you get{nl}
the feeling we did something{nl}
uncalled-for?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Afros are in fashion,{nl}
are they... Maybe I'll try an{nl}
afro too.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Kozai and I are a little{nl}
alike.{wait_fr:32} ...Does that surprise{nl}
you?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: They say if the Queen{nl}
takes a liking to you, you{nl}
get to live easy~!{waitkey}{clearbox}Just leave it to me! Any girl{nl}
will go down for my charms,{nl}
for sure!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Kozai had this kinda{nl}
blue around her eyes...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
...It was scary~!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: A cheeky little brat{nl}
like that lives in a castle?{nl}
You've got to be kidding!{waitkey}{clearbox}A castle suits a sophisticated{nl}
man like me, and me alone!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Kozai doesn't even{nl}
know the real Sonomura is{nl}
suffering...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: She's so pretty, so{nl}
what's Kozai got to complain{nl}
about? Ayase's fine as she is.{waitkey}{clearbox}Not that I'm a beauty, but{nl}
freckles are cute too. A{nl}
"funny face," you could say?{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: In any case, unless we{nl}
find a way out of here, we{nl}
can't move forward, is that{nl}
it?{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Honestly, you and{nl}
Sonomura are both hopeless{nl}
softies.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: At times like this,{nl}
nothing anyone says helps...{nl}
you've just got to sort it{nl}
out yourself.{waitkey}{ret}

Clerk: Why not become strong{nl}
and beautiful like the Queen,{nl}
with our shop's armor?{waitkey}{ret}

Clerk: Absolutely essential{nl}
for surviving this world! For{nl}
all your armor needs, leave{nl}
it to us.{waitkey}{ret}

Customer: We're stuck in this{nl}
market anyway, the lot of us!{waitkey}{clearbox}Might as well keep the Queen{nl}
happy and live it up while{nl}
we can!{waitkey}{ret}

Customer: We don't have to{nl}
keep the Queen happy anymore,{nl}
right? But somehow it's a{nl}
little lonely!{waitkey}{ret}
